# 📖 Chapter 15 – Google Search Console (GSC)

---

# 🎯 Chapter Objective

Is chapter me hum Google Search Console (GSC) ko detail me samjhenge. Aap seekhenge ki Google Search Console kya hota hai, website ko verify kaise karte hain, indexing kaise monitor karte hain, performance reports kaise analyze karte hain aur SEO improve karne ke liye GSC ka practical use kaise kiya jata hai.

---

# 15.1 What is Google Search Console?

**Google Search Console (GSC)** Google ka free tool hai jo website owners ko website ki search performance monitor aur improve karne me help karta hai.

Simple Words:

> **Google Search Console = Google aur aapki website ke beech communication tool.**

Ye batata hai:

* Website Google me kaise perform kar rahi hai.
* Kaunse pages index hue hain.
* Kaunse keywords par impressions aur clicks aa rahe hain.
* Kaunse technical issues hain.

---

# 15.2 Why Google Search Console is Important?

Har SEO professional ke liye GSC mandatory tool hai.

Benefits:

* Website Performance Monitor
* Indexing Status Check
* Keyword Analysis
* Technical SEO Issues
* Sitemap Submission
* Mobile Usability Insights
* Search Performance Tracking

---

