# 15.4 Property Types

Google Search Console me do types ki properties hoti hain.

## Domain Property

Pure domain ko cover karti hai.

Example:

```text id="7r6v0h"
safeprofire.com
```

Includes:

* www
* non-www
* http
* https
* Subdomains

Recommended for most websites.

---

## URL Prefix Property

Specific URL version ko track karti hai.

Example:

```text id="8q4s6m"
https://www.safeprofire.com
```

---

# 15.5 Website Verification

Website verify karne ke common methods:

* DNS Record
* HTML File Upload
* HTML Meta Tag
* Google Analytics
* Google Tag Manager

Verification complete hone ke baad reports available hoti hain.

---

# 15.6 Performance Report

Performance Report sabse important report hai.

Ye metrics show karti hai:

* Clicks
* Impressions
* CTR (Click-Through Rate)
* Average Position

Example:

| Metric      | Meaning                                          |
| ----------- | ------------------------------------------------ |
| Clicks      | Kitne users ne click kiya                        |
| Impressions | Kitni baar page search results me dikha          |
| CTR         | Impression ke comparison me clicks ka percentage |
| Position    | Average Google ranking position                  |

---

# 15.7 URL Inspection Tool

Is tool se check kar sakte hain:

* Page indexed hai ya nahi.
* Last crawl kab hua.
* Mobile-friendly hai ya nahi.
* Live Test pass karta hai ya nahi.

Agar page index nahi hua ho to indexing request bhej sakte hain.

---

# 15.8 Indexing Report

Ye report batati hai:

* Indexed Pages
* Non-Indexed Pages
* Crawl Errors
* Excluded Pages

Goal:

Maximum important pages index hone chahiye.

---

# 15.9 XML Sitemap Submission

Google ko sitemap submit karne se crawling aur indexing improve ho sakti hai.

Example:

```text id="m8w5tk"
https://www.safeprofire.com/sitemap.xml
```

Submit karne ke baad status monitor karte raho.

