# 15.13 Manual Actions

Agar Google website par spam ya policy violation detect kare to Manual Action de sakta hai.

Common Reasons:

* Spam Content
* Unnatural Backlinks
* Cloaking
* Hidden Text

Manual Actions ko jaldi resolve karna chahiye.

